sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Entry as 入口脚本
    participant Builder as PipelineBuilder
    participant Pipeline as Pipeline
    participant Read as Read
    participant Parse as Parse
    participant Extract as Extract
    participant Enrich as Enrich
    participant Write as Write

    User->>Entry: --input ... --output ...
    Entry->>Builder: build_pipeline(config)
    Builder-->>Pipeline: 构建完成的管道
    Entry->>Pipeline: run(config)

    Pipeline->>Read: process(config)
    Note right of Read: TC: TestCaseJsonReader 扫描 JSON 文件夹, 仅提取 metadata<br/>AW: AWJsonReader 读取文件路径列表, 加载源文件
    Read-->>Pipeline: TC: List[Dict] / AW: List[RawSourceFile]

    Pipeline->>Parse: process(read_data)
    Note right of Parse: TC: TestCaseClassParseStage 读取源文件, AST 定位 ClassDef<br/>AW: ASTParseStage + AWParser 解析 aw_* 函数
    Parse-->>Pipeline: TC: List[(metadata, class_name, class_node, source_lines)]<br/>AW: List[Tuple]

    Pipeline->>Extract: process(parsed_data)
    Note right of Extract: TC: TestCaseCorpusParseStage 语句层级遍历, tc.logInfo 作 prompt 分隔符, 控制流块递归提取<br/>AW: DocstringExtractStage + AWDocstringParser 解析 docstring 提取功能描述
    Extract-->>Pipeline: TC: List[(metadata, class_name, List[CodePair])]<br/>AW: List[Tuple]

    Pipeline->>Enrich: process(extracted_data)
    Note right of Enrich: TC: TestCaseEnrichStage FIELD_MAPPING 映射输入到输出字段, 填充 TestCaseCorpusItem<br/>AW: AWEnrichStage 组装 AWCorpusItem
    Enrich-->>Pipeline: TC: List[TestCaseCorpusItem] / AW: List[AWCorpusItem]

    Pipeline->>Write: process(corpus_items)
    Note right of Write: TC: TestCaseFileWriter 以 test_case_number 命名, 每用例一个 JSON<br/>AW: AWAggregateWriter 聚合输出单个 JSON
    Write-->>Pipeline: 输出目录路径

    Pipeline-->>Entry: 完成
    Entry-->>User: 输出路径
